-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-BHP Billiton, Galenica AG  
-- 
-- Tue Oct 21, 2014 03:44AM EDT
-- None



Oct 21 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including BHP Billiton, Galenica AG and Statoil, on Tuesday.

